&lt;p&gt;《&lt;a href=&quot;http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MjAzODU2MA==&amp;amp;mid=2652781703&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=2eb2bcf3a3a541b1727acfbe8453f797&amp;amp;chksm=bd46f7488a317e5eba6aff485ad428f0a1f34582c4eb6c7f243f80ed84c8b2c842a289bfef2b&amp;amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;谢逊盲测·五国牛排篇（完整版）&lt;/a&gt;》&lt;/p&gt;
