&lt;p&gt;《&lt;a href=&quot;http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MjAzODU2MA==&amp;amp;mid=2652781707&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=7f01e693b98cfb47984ef15b5cca6be5&amp;amp;chksm=bd46f7448a317e52b39efdc9fa2bba5d87534550d0e2a737a8dce9d8c169b643644380b1e8fd&amp;amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;生日快乐，和菜头先生&lt;/a&gt;》&lt;/p&gt;
